summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the improvement of the alleys adjoining Blocks 17, 18, 23, 24, 25, 26 and 27, replat of Green Lake Home Addition, and adjoining Block 1, Weaver's Green Lake Addition, being the alleys in the block bounded by East Green Lake Drive North, Stroud Avenue North, North 80th Street, Meridian Avenue North and North 78th Street; by paving the same, etc.
